{"tid":2198848,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)GTA5","createTime":"2020-09-11T16:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T18:04:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed3c25e994d445752c271673494bbd128313f79","tid":2198848,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3frCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=3dd6abcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3frCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=abe9e652\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<img src=\"https://image-cdn.essentiallysports.com/wp-content/uploads/20200807220259/maxresdefault-8-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage-cdn.essentiallysports.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20200807220259%2Fmaxresdefault-8-4.jpg&h=1479af8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《俠盜獵車手V》是一款第三人稱開放世界動作冒險遊戲。玩者可通過完成帶設定目標的任務場景，使故事取得進展[15]。除了做任務，玩家可自由徜徉開放世界裡&mdash;&mdash;從開闊的鄉村地區布雷恩，到虛構城市洛聖都。《俠盜獵車手V》的地圖比系列的任一早期作品都大[16]。地圖從一開始就可不受限制地探索，但隨著劇情的發展，會有更多的遊戲內容解鎖[17]。玩者使用拳腳近身攻擊、槍械、武器和炸彈等來與敵人戰鬥，並能夠以跑步、跳躍、游泳和駕駛各種載具等方式瀏覽地圖。為適應地圖的大小，本作引入了《俠盜獵車手IV》中缺席的固定翼飛機。遊戲提供了自動瞄準和躲避系統來幫助玩家與敵人戰鬥。[18]若主角受傷，其健康值將恢復到中間點。玩者透過完成一連串的任務來推進遊戲的故事內容，與大多數的開放世界類型的遊戲相同，玩者可自由選擇在任何時間去執行這些任務。如果玩者在遊戲中進行了任何違法行為，遊戲中的警察機構可能會採取行動，遊戲右上角將會顯示玩者被「通緝」的程度[19]。當玩者持續進行違法行為時，用來代表通緝程度的星號將會增加，警察對於玩家的追緝也會隨之變得更加激烈<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3frCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=d807e6c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3frCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=6e3e9c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35ab9f3847becbe31c7d314c6172d40c8e595fa","tid":2198848,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e82f944b96655a9b29d1f64362478e3a0035be","tid":2198848,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}